---
---
<section class="bg-white py-20" aria-label="Bônus inclusos">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">

    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="badge bg-accent-light text-accent mb-3 w-fit mx-auto">Só para quem comprar agora</span>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-ink gsap-reveal">
        Olha só os bônus especiais que preparei!
      </h2>
      <span class="ink-divider block mx-auto mt-4" style="max-width:100px"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

      <!-- Bônus 1 -->
      <div class="gsap-reveal-left bg-surface-warm rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 flex flex-col">
        <!-- Mockup sem shadow (fundo provavelmente branco/transparente) -->
        <img
          src="/imgs/paginas-internas/mockup-365-branding-bonus-365-making-planilha.avif"
          alt="Planilha 365 Making — Bônus incluso"
          width="500" height="280"
          loading="lazy"
          class="w-full h-48 object-contain bg-surface-card"
        />
        <div class="p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col">
          <span class="badge bg-accent-light text-accent w-fit mb-3">Bônus 01</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-xl text-brand-ink mb-2">Planilha 365 Making</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Planilha no Google Drive com o compilado de todos os 365 exercícios em calendário organizado.
            Marque e visualize ao longo do ano quais ações já colocou em prática.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm line-through">R$197</span>
            <span class="badge bg-accent-light text-accent">Incluso gratuitamente</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bônus 2 -->
      <div class="gsap-reveal-right bg-surface-warm rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 flex flex-col">
        <div class="w-full h-48 bg-brand-navy flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center text-white">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-accent/20 border-2 border-accent flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent ml-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-heading font-bold text-lg">MasterClass</p>
            <p class="text-accent text-sm">3 horas de conteúdo</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col">
          <span class="badge bg-accent-light text-accent w-fit mb-3">Bônus 02</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-xl text-brand-ink mb-2">MasterClass de Planejamento Estratégico</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed flex-1">
            3 horas gravadas na área de membros. O que considerar em branding na hora de planejar?
            Quais os primeiros passos? Como fazer na prática?
          </p>
          <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm line-through">R$197</span>
            <span class="badge bg-accent-light text-accent">Incluso gratuitamente</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12 gsap-reveal">
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn-shimmer inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent text-white font-heading font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-accent-dark transition-colors duration-300">
        Quero o 365DB com todos os bônus!
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
